<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My First Code - #MyFirstCode</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            text-align: center;
            animation: slideUp 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .emoji {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .code-preview {
            background: #f4f4f4;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
            text-align: left;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }

        .date {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="emoji">🚀</div>
        <h1>Hello World!</h1>
        <p>
            This is my <span class="highlight">first line of code</span> and it feels amazing! 
            My GitHub certificate journey starts right here.
        </p>
        <div class="badge">#MyFirstCode ✅</div>
        <div class="code-preview">
            &lt;h1&gt;Hello World!&lt;/h1&gt;<br>
            &lt;p&gt;I'm learning to code 🎯&lt;/p&gt;
        </div>
        <div class="date">April 22, 2026</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
